text: Lipus or LIPUS may refer to: *Cvetka Lipuš (born 1966), an Austrian poet writing in Slovenian *Florjan Lipuš (born 1937), a Carinthian Slovene writer *Low intensity pulsed ultrasound (LIPUS), a medical technology *LIPUS = Loging - Insert - (Preview - Update) - Search (LIPUS), an IT technology
